Usage: setProbePin [-help] {{-instName <instName> -pinName <pinName>} | -bump <bumpName>}

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-bump <bumpName>         # specifies the name of bump (string, required)
-instName <instName>     # specifies the name of I/O instance
                         # (string, required)
-pinName <pinName>       # specifies the name of pin on I/O instance
                         # (string, required)